description: Jeremiah's Italian Ice is the place to go for delicious frozen treats! Looking for the coolest catering option in town? The Jeremiah's Team can scoop up our refreshing Italian Ice at your next special event! Our full service food truck affords the opportunity to bring our fun & exciting frozen dessert experience directly to you. This big green machine is sure to grab attention and serves up the tastiest sweets on the street! Jeremiah's is a refreshing option for any event! We have over 40+ flavors of Italian Ice, vanilla, chocolate, and swirl soft serve ice cream, and our famous gelatis. Check out our sample menu and don't forget to Life Life to the Coolest!
name: Jeremiah's Italian Ice
